{"tid":1975336,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社工呂智恆司法覆核指監警會涉越權敗訴　需支付訟費","createTime":"2020-04-16T12:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T13:02:03.000Z","uid":48409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f828efc8157a488a409f2773dd659fc09899ea6","tid":1975336,"uid":48409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"社工呂智恆早前申請司法覆核，要求裁定監警會審視去年6月起發生的大型示威活動，是超越監警會權限，高等法院裁定，監警會並無越權，判呂智恆敗訴，需支付訟費。<br />\n<br />\n高等法院法官楊家雄於判詞中表示，除非列明是禁止進行，否則於法例上都應該被視為容許，認為監警會的研究中，所進行的尋找事實過程，並無超越監警會權限，但他不會在判詞中，全面說明監警會於法律下能夠做的事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520953-20200416.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520953-20200416.htm&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10JdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=d899798d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520953-20200416.htm&h=49d5bdcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520953-20200416.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTQQgLG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTQQgLG.jpg&h=94019dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c497949fce5d2d57b9b2451536d18cdeb06a8d","tid":1975336,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:51:33.000Z","msg":"其實者係咩意思呢？證明監豬會係癈?"},{"pid":"5cd184e20a3dc691e3ce881a80c5bf3725b69781","tid":1975336,"uid":51183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"高等法院法官楊家雄於判詞中表示，除非列明是禁止進行，否則於法例上都應該被視為容許<br />\n<br />\n區議會快D告民政署班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}